---
title: Family-Style Dilly Chicken Thighs & Rice 2x the delicious portions!
description: The flavors of the Mediterranean star in this easy meal for a crowd. You’ll serve juicy, dill-seasoned roasted chicken thighs over buttery rice, with a side of simple salt-and-pepper-roasted green beans and tomatoes. A creamy, lemony cucumber-dill tzatziki-style sauce rounds out this savory spread for dipping and drizzling as you like. This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663a6fb6fe8a253ad9a7a9e7-686355f0.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/663a6fb6fe8a253ad9a7a9e7-en-US.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: Southern Europe
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/family-style-dilly-chicken-thighs-and-rice-663a6fb6fe8a253ad9a7a9e7
time required: 40 minutes
author: HelloFresh
